<h1>Flickr User Claim Approved</h1>

<p>
  A user has successfully verified their Flickr account automatically.
</p>

<h2>Details</h2>

<p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Photonia User:</strong> <%= h @user.email %> (#<%= h @user.serial_number %>)</li>
    <li><strong>Flickr Username:</strong> <%= h @flickr_user.username %></li>
    <li><strong>Flickr NSID:</strong> <%= h @flickr_user.nsid %></li>
    <li><strong>Flickr Profile:</strong> <a href="<%= h @flickr_user.profileurl %>"><%= h @flickr_user.profileurl %></a></li>
    <li><strong>Claim Type:</strong> Automatic</li>
    <li><strong>Status:</strong> Approved</li>
    <li><strong>Verified At:</strong> <%= @claim.verified_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z') %></li>
  </ul>
</p>

<h2>User Details</h2>

<p>
  You can view the user's details here:
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @user_admin_url %>">View User in Admin Panel</a>
</p>

<p>
  Your friendly Photonia bot.
</p>
